title: Battle of the Black Gate: Eagle Reinforcements - Total War: WARHAMMER Gameplay
description:
It's time to witness another lord of the Rings inspired battle in Total War: WARHAMMER.  This time the Empire and Bretonnia march an army to the Black Gate.  The Greenskins sally out of the gate to swallow Empire and Bretonnia whole, but eagle reinforcements are on their way!  Enjoy the Battle :D 

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
